description: Tangiamo Touch Technology AB engages in the provision of information technology services. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands. The company went IPO on 2017-04-06. The technology applies primarily in casino industry in tables where the bids are managed. The firm operates in three segments: Touch Technology, Electronic Table Games and Online Gaming. The Touch Technology segment refers to technology product that sells to hardware manufacturers and implies various applications. The Electronic Table Games segment comprises operations for casino industry. The Online Gaming segment implies development of diverse forms of online gambling. The firm sells its products through selected distributors and directly in more than 30 countries.
naics: Semiconductor and Other Electronic Component Manufacturing
name: Tangiamo Touch Technology AB
